high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the dining table.
Pick up tomato from the dining table.
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the fridge.
Place tomato on the fridge.
Turn around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the dining table.
Pick up tomato from the dining table.
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the fridge.
Place tomato on the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Collecting tomato from different places and arranging them on a fridge.

high_descs: Turn around to the right and walk to the right side of the diningtable.
Pick up the tomato on the right side of the microwave on the table.
With the tomato, go to the fridge, which is on the right of the microwave.
Open the fridge, place the tomato nearby the front opening corner on the bottom floor, then close the fridge.
Return to the diningtable area and face to the front of microwave.
Pick up the tomato in front of the spatula on table.
With the tomato, go back to the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the tomato behind the other tomato and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place two Tomato in the Fridge.

high_descs: Turn right. Reach the diningtable and turn right. Turn left to the wall and then left.
Grab the tomato.
Turn left. Continue ahead. Then turn left until you reach the fridge. Turn left.
Open the fridge. Place the tomato on the first level on the left side. Close the fridge.
Make a left turn. Then turn left. Go forward to the diningtable. Turn right to be in front of the diningtable.
Grab the tomato.
Turn right. Reach the bottom. Turn left to be in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge. Place the tomato on the left, next to the other tomato. Close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Search for two tomatoes. Place them in the fridge.
